[26/04/2019 14:59:22] <font color="#ffffff">Muy bien.</font>
[26/04/2019 14:59:22] <font color="#ffff00">¿"Tot molt bé"?</font>
[26/04/2019 14:59:23] <font color="#ffffff">Sí, "tutto bene, tutto bene".</font>
[26/04/2019 14:59:26] <font color="#ffff00">¿Has visto?</font>
